## Agent loop

```
── boot() ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
← { contract_etag, writable_lanes: [<%= writable_agent_lanes.map{|l|l["name"]}.join(", ") %>],
    propose_lane: "<%= propose_lane %>", latest_seq: N }

── [per turn] ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
── pulse() → { cursor, changed: [...], pending_review: [...] }
── list / get for anything in changed
── put / propose based on work

── [contract changes mid-session] ─────────────────────────────────────
── put() → contract_drift error (-32001)
── boot() → { contract_etag: "sha256:new", latest_seq: M }
── [resume writing]
```

